## Current Focus: Stage 2 - Backend Hardening

---

## Stage 1: Backend Hardening
**Duration**: 7-10 days | **Priority**: P0 | **Status**: 🔄 In Progress

### Rate Limiting & Security
- [x] Add `express-rate-limit` to all API routes
- [x] Implement account lockout after 5 failed login attempts
- [x] Add IP-based rate limiting for OTP requests
- [x] Create brute-force protection middleware

### Auth Enhancements
- [ ] Implement password reset flow (send email with reset token)
- [ ] Add email verification for new accounts
- [ ] Multi-device session management (list/revoke sessions)
- [ ] Add session activity logging

### API Improvements
- [x] Add API versioning (`/api/v1/` prefix)
- [x] Implement request ID tracking (correlation IDs)
- [x] Add request/response logging middleware
- [x] Standardize error response format

