## Stage 3: Infrastructure (Terraform)
**Duration**: 8-10 days | **Priority**: P0

### Network Layer
- [ ] Define VPC with public/private subnets
- [ ] Create security groups for each tier
- [ ] Setup NAT gateway for private subnets
- [ ] Configure route tables

### Compute & Container
- [ ] Create ECS cluster (Fargate)
- [ ] Setup ECR for Docker images
- [ ] Create ECS task definitions
- [ ] Configure ECS services with ALB

### Data Layer
- [ ] Configure MongoDB Atlas connection
- [ ] Setup ElastiCache (Redis) cluster
- [ ] Create S3 buckets (media, backups)
- [ ] Setup CloudFront distribution

### DNS & SSL
- [ ] Setup Route 53 hosted zone
- [ ] Create ACM certificates
- [ ] Configure ALB HTTPS listener

### Outputs
- [ ] Create Terraform modules structure
- [ ] Setup S3 backend for state
- [ ] Document variables and outputs

